    {
      "id": "01aa28f5-32eb-4a41-88da-3a71fc69eeed",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On pose pour $(x,y)\\in\\R^2$~:\n$$f(x,y) = x^2+y^2-2x^2y - \\frac{4x^6y^2}{(x^4+y^2)^2}\\quad\\text{si }(x,y)\\ne 0,\n  \\qquad f(0,0)=0.$$",
        "html": "<p>On pose pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y)\\in\\R^2\\)</span> : <span class=\"math display\">\\[f(x,y) = x^2+y^2-2x^2y - \\frac{4x^6y^2}{(x^4+y^2)^2}\\quad\\text{si }(x,y)\\ne 0,\n  \\qquad f(0,0)=0.\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "113c79b0-d007-4a49-81b8-1c46b577678a",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $f$ est continue sur $\\R^2$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est continue sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\R^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "43482029-b027-4312-97cb-9c13f64d7cee",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$2x^4y^2 \\le (x^4+y^2)^2$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(2x^4y^2 \\le (x^4+y^2)^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0f627f84-3f4c-4de4-af31-1ad603a20213",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $\\theta\\in\\R$ fixé et $g_\\theta(r) = f(r\\cos\\theta,r\\sin\\theta)$.\nMontrer que $g_\\theta$ admet un minimum local strict en~$r=0$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\theta\\in\\R\\)</span> fixé et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(g_\\theta(r) = f(r\\cos\\theta,r\\sin\\theta)\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(g_\\theta\\)</span> admet un minimum local strict en <span class=\"math inline\">\\(r=0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "64287689-3235-4b04-87f7-61cc34372383",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$g_\\theta(r)\\sim r^2$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(g_\\theta(r)\\sim r^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6b890503-ff42-4575-8f20-2d6e71c24940",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $f(x,x^2)$. Conclusion~?",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,x^2)\\)</span>. Conclusion ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "504c8c85-0c28-4fc3-ad6c-61c2e7959b53",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$f(x,x^2)=-x^4$. Donc $(0,0)$ n'est pas minimum local de~$f$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,x^2)=-x^4\\)</span>. Donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\((0,0)\\)</span> n’est pas minimum local de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
